node.text: BTS of my latest shoot with the #djipocket2 ! @djiglobal sent me their new #sunsetwhite addition, which was amazing with its multiple intelligent features such as timelapse, hyperlapse, and slow motion which helps me continue to take my creative content to the next level. Even better, the DJI Pocket 2 is perfect for beginners with its portable size and awesome 3 axis motorized stabilization. Click in the link in my bio to get your own DJI Pocket 2! AD

node.text: #ad I've partnered with @lenovo to work on their #lenovo Yoga 7i, which allows me to go back and forth between a tablet and laptop while working on the road. Not only is the device extremely portable, but it's vibrant visuals and Dolby Atmos sound ensures that editing content is a breeze. To learn more about the Lenovo Yoga 7i, click the link in my bio #windows10home

node.text:
One year ago, we decided to buy a van..
I’ve partnered with @lg_global to showcase a meaningful place in my life. If you submit footage and it makes it to the final film, you’ll be entered for a chance to win an LG gram and your name will be in the credits. To learn more about the "Life is Good" campaign, click here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JSKl5MiNGf8. 
The entry period goes until July 4th, 2021 at 11:59 p.m. (EDT)

#LifeisGood #LifeisGoodFilm_LG #LG #Film #JacksonTisi ad #vanlife #campervan #travel #travelfilm #tinyhome #explore #travelmore #couple #videography #photography #roadtrip
